OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FBritain is facing the longest
OL,8,Fsustained rise in sickness-related
OL,9,Finactivity since the 1990s, with a
OL,10,Fnear record 2.7 million working-age
OL,11,Fadults too sick to work, a think tank
OL,12,Fsays.
OL,14,FThe Resolution Foundation says
OL,15,Feconomic inactivity due to long-term
OL,16,Fsickness has increased on an annual
OL,17,Fbasis since July 2019, the longest
OL,18,Fsustained rise since 1994-1998.JA new
OL,19,Fstudy by the think tank finds that
OL,20,Fincreases are concentrated among the
OL,21,Fyoungest and oldest workers.
